[h3 id=LastThoughts/InTheFuture 
	"Last Thoughts/In The Future
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/Truncated 
		"Truncated
	]a
	": If you think this took a long time, consider how long it would have taken for one person... at least if that one person had been me. Having a partner really helped, both for sharing the workload and for motivating me to soldier on when I hit a stumper. Having two runs made it easy to work in parallel. Also I feel our skillsets complemented each other well. All in all it was a fun time! I hope you enjoy the result!
	$LF
]p
[p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/VANDAL 
		"VANDAL
	]a
	": I had a lot of fun working on this project which was mostly because I was able to work with someone.  Sure, it took longer but it sure made the runs extra special.  In the future, I hope to work on Bloodlines again with, most likely, Truncated but that won't be for a while, at least on my part.  Here's hoping you guys enjoy as it took more than a year to complete.  See you all later.
	$LF
]p
